name: #03 Flying Dora (SPACERUNNERS)
description: 3rd edition of the SPACERUNNERS collection. In this issue, you will meet flying Dora from the planet K2-18b. Unlike other astronauts, Dora has a hovercycle and therefore does not run, but flies. SPACERUNNERS is a collection of running astronauts. Is a continuation of the SPACEWALKERS collection. All the heroes of the previous issues got out of the boxes and now explore the expanses of space!
